commit.message:
Merge branch 'develop' into feature/sim-cam-work

* develop:
  Fixes DrawTemplateMatches stage drawing at corner rather than centered.
  Added support to enable Linux to detect and use the /dev/serial/by-id device names to allow consistent port choice.
  * Removed extraneous calls to VisionUtils.getBottomVisionCamera(). * Fixed an error with calculating the speed the nozzle should move at. Part speed is already applied in ReferenceNozzle, the code would have caused it to move at part speed ^ -2. * Added comments about magic numbers. * Fixed minor text errors.
  Fix up formatting.
  Fixes #589 by checking for null in SimulatedUpCamera when machine activity happens.
  Update ReferenceBottomVision.java
  Update ReferencePnpJobProcessor.java
  Update ReferenceBottomVisionConfigurationWizard.java
  Update ReferenceBottomVisionPartConfigurationWizard.java
  fix prerotate,
